title: Annes Secret Recipe Chocolate Fudge 300G
description:
Annes
Secret Recipe Chocolate Fudge
300G
You will need:
-1/2 Cup Vegetable Oil
-2 Large Eggs
-2/3 Cup Milk
1.Heat
Oven to 160C,Use papercups to line a 12 cupcakes baking tray.
2.Beat
Cake mix,eggs,milk and oil in a large bowl on LOW speed for 30secs.Increase speed to HIGH and beat for 3mins.
3.Bake
At 160C for 10-15mins. Insert toothpick in the center,should come out clean when done. Cool 10min before frosting.
4.Final Product
Add Chocolate Fudge on cupcake and decorate.
